reviewText: My grandchildren really enjoy this movie.
This was a gift for my granddaughter and she loved it!
I really enjoyed watching this with my grandson!
My granddaughter love herself some Barney so anything with that character gets her excited. Of course, I love it because she does.
Best Barney Ever - my Toddler loves this one and sings along to all the songs it's so cute! :) enjoyable for everyone

This is long overdue as a kid I loved this movie and I still do, I would play this vhs along with the others over and over again. I had all the toys and books from the movie too it's not exactly your usual Barney movie but it's still "Super Dee Duper" Do your kids a favor and buy this movie!!!
